sense.name: 十二月, December
sense.commentary: the twelfth and last month of the year.
sense.examples:
十二月五号 December fifth.
十二月我们将去欧洲。 In the December we will go to Europe.

sense.name: 十二月， the twelfth moon.
sense.commentary: The twelfth moon of the lunar year.
sense.examples:
中国农历十二月 The twelfth month of the lunar year.
农历第十二个月。 The twelfth moon.
